<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <title>About Us - Bookstore App</title>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Bookstore App</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/addbooks">Add new books</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                        <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" id="navbarDropdown" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                            Genres
                        </a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="navbarDropdown">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/genres/Fantasy">Fantasy</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/genres/Science%20Fiction">Science Fiction</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/genres/Comedy">Comedy</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/genres/Fiction">Fiction</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/genres/Comic">Comic</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/genres/Adventure">Adventure</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About Us</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <form class="d-flex ms-auto" action="/search" method="GET">
                    <input class="form-control me-2" type="search" name="query" placeholder="Search for books" aria-label="Search">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-success" type="submit">Search</button>
                    <a href="/cart" class="btn btn-outline-primary ms-2">
                        <i class="bi bi-cart"></i> <!-- Bootstrap Icons cart icon -->
                    </a>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        
        <!-- Mission Section -->
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h2>Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to inspire and enrich lives through the joy of reading. We aim to provide a welcoming space where book lovers of all ages can discover, explore, and indulge in the world of literature. Through curated selections, knowledgeable staff, and community engagement, we strive to foster a love for reading and lifelong learning.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Vision Section -->
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h2>Vision</h2>
            <p>Our vision is to be the preferred destination for book enthusiasts, a place where creativity thrives, knowledge expands, and stories come to life. We envision a bookstore that serves as a hub for cultural exchange, intellectual curiosity, and literary discovery, continually evolving to meet the diverse interests and needs of our community.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Team Section -->
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <!-- CEO Card -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/aarvalan.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="CEO Picture">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CEO</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">The CEO of a bookstore is typically the top executive responsible for overseeing the overall operations and strategic direction of the business.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- CFO Card -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/jaron.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="CFO Picture">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CFO</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">As the CFO of a bookstore, this executive is in charge of financial planning, monitoring cash flow, and managing financial risks.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- COO Card -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/sleepy.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="COO Picture">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">COO</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">The COO of a bookstore oversees the day-to-day operations and logistics to ensure smooth and efficient functioning of the bookstore. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/joseph.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="COO Picture">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Tech Support</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Tech support in a bookstore environment plays a critical role in maintaining and troubleshooting the bookstore's technological infrastructure.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
